(13, 'About us', '[{\"type\":\"call_to_action\",\"name\":\"Call To Action\",\"model\":{\"title\":\"Call To Action\",\"sub_title\":\"tripraja.com is an online travel\",\"link_title\":\"Title Link More\",\"link_more\":\"#\",\"style\":\"style_2\",\"bg_image\":364,\"list_item\":[]},\"component\":\"RegularBlock\",\"open\":true,\"is_container\":false},{\"type\":\"list_locations\",\"name\":\"List Locations\",\"model\":{\"layout\":\"style_3\",\"service_type\":[\"tour\",\"event\"],\"title\":\"Title\",\"desc\":\"Desc Desc \",\"number\":4,\"order\":\"\",\"order_by\":\"\",\"custom_ids\":\"\",\"to_location_detail\":true,\"view_all_url\":\"\"},\"component\":\"RegularBlock\",\"open\":true,\"is_container\":false},{\"type\":\"text\",\"name\":\"Text\",\"model\":{\"content\":\"<h2>About tripraja.com</h2>\\n<p>Established in the year 2015, tripraja.com is an online travel and adventure tour company, which emerged as a one-stop destination for wanderlust souls to fulfil their travel bucket list wishes. The main idea behind starting our company is a belief that money doesn&rsquo;t make you rich but memorable experiences do. tripraja.com was started with an aim to boost the subject of travel and adventure tourism. With a strong presence in the inbound travel trade and tourism, we strive to excel in all the services we provide. We offer our clients adventure tourism, cruising, sightseeing, and excursion facilities in the most alluring and seamless ways.</p>\",\"class\":\"bg-blue-2\"},\"component\":\"RegularBlock\",\"open\":true,\"is_container\":false},{\"type\":\"about_text\",\"name\":\"About Text\",\"model\":{\"title\":\"Why Choose us ?\",\"desc\":\"completely dedicated to meet the needs\",\"content\":\"We are community of adventurous souls who are completely dedicated to meet the needs and thirst of people who want to travel around for adventure and nature. So here are some of the reasons why you should put your trust in us. \\n\\n\",\"bg_image\":379,\"list_item\":[]},\"component\":\"Reg